\fs32 \cf2 Like we did with the Splurty web application, before we start coding, let's first:\'a0
\b setup our web development pipeline
\b0 \'a0so we can back-up our code frequently and push changes to our application live onto our server on the internet.\
With that in mind, lets start our new project by setting up our pipeline and connecting it to GitHub (to keep our code safe) & heroku (our server, to go live onto the internet).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl320\partightenfactor0

